# =============================================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# =============================================================================

# Common Issues:
# 1. AWS Bedrock access denied: Ensure IAM user has bedrock:InvokeModel permission
# 2. Database connection failed: Check credentials and network access
# 3. No F1 data found: Ensure CSV files are in formula1-datasets/ directory
# 4. Embedding errors: Verify model name and AWS region

# Support:
# - Check logs with DEBUG_MODE=true
# - Run npm run check-setup for diagnostics
